Class SecurityContextAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microbean.jersey.netty.SecurityContextAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SecurityContext

    public class SecurityContextAdapter
extends Object
implements SecurityContext
    A fallback SecurityContext implementation that provides no user Principal, has no role or user database, is not secure, and that does not require authentication.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson
